title: [Bottom of the Well]
description: The damp stone walls of the well rise steeply, ending in a dark circle of star-filled sky.  Water trickles down the stone walls and drips onto the muddy floor with a soft, repetitious plop.  On the southern wall is the entrance to a narrow tunnel.

The damp stone walls of the well rise steeply, ending in a bright blue circle of cloudless sky.  Water trickles down the stone walls and drips onto the muddy floor with a soft, repetitious plop.  On the southern wall is the entrance to a low tunnel.
